@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei

title 配置文件工作流程

actor 用户 as User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "ConfigLoader" as Loader
participant "Scheduler" as Scheduler
database "config.yaml" as Config
database "memory/" as Memory

== 1. 创建配置 ==
User -> CLI: create-task
CLI -> Config: 生成模板
Config --> User: config.yaml

note right of Config
基本结构:
- project_name
- project_path
- mode (serial/parallel/loop)
- tasks[]
end note

== 2. 编辑配置 ==
User -> Config: 编辑 config.yaml
note right of User
配置任务:
- id, description
- prompt_template
- expected_output
- depends_on (可选)
end note

== 3. 验证配置 ==
User -> CLI: --config config.yaml run --dry-run
CLI -> Loader: 加载配置
Loader -> Loader: 验证字段
alt 配置有效
    Loader --> CLI: ✓ 配置有效
    CLI --> User: 显示执行计划
else 配置无效
    Loader --> CLI: ✗ 错误信息
    CLI --> User: 显示错误
    User -> Config: 修复配置
end

== 4. 执行任务 ==
User -> CLI: --config config.yaml run
CLI -> Loader: 加载配置
Loader -> Scheduler: 创建调度器
Scheduler -> Memory: 初始化记忆
Memory --> Scheduler: 记忆就绪

loop 每个任务
    Scheduler -> Scheduler: 执行任务
    Scheduler -> Memory: 更新记忆
end

Scheduler --> CLI: 执行完成
CLI --> User: 显示结果

== 5. 恢复执行 ==
User -> CLI: resume --project-name xxx
CLI -> Memory: 加载状态
Memory --> Scheduler: 恢复上下文
Scheduler -> Scheduler: 继续执行

@enduml
